Church 2017-05-04

10 commandments to believers 

I am the Lord God who created the heavens and the earth and brought you out of the land of Egypt, -- before each of the commandments 

You shall have no other gods before me
		gods goal is to enslave God's people
		It's a good thing to be human
		God made you with desires - these are connectors

When you're addicted, you're enslaved to the god you chose to serve

What to do:
		monitor competitors
		Do biopsy on your desires
		Audit on your calendar - how much time connecting with God
		Check your "heat" index - what's going on in your heart? How's your desire for Jesus?
